modules.description: Parses and generates HTTP multipart/form-data bodies using streaming to handle large files without excessive memory use. Works with byte streams and content type headers to process data in chunks. Enables efficient file uploads and form data handling in web applications.

Processes multipart/form-data streams by parsing and extracting parts, storing content in memory. Works with Eio.Stream.t and Multipart_form.Header.t to handle HTTP multipart data. Enables saving stream parts to files or converting the entire stream into a structured in-memory representation.
